Privacy Policy
Last updated: February 21, 2023
REN WATCHFACES is a developer who designs watch faces for Tizen OS and Wear OS. We care about your privacy and security of your personal information.
Collecting and Using your Personal Data
RENS WATCHFACES does not collect, store or share user data to any of our watch faces and apps available on Play Store. We do not store any personal data and share with any third party company.
Installing watch faces needs permission in order for complications to function properly on the watch, these are heart rate, steps, weather, calendar, battery level. Check these permissions on your watch and phone in the app info.
Children's Privacy
RENS WATCHFACES does not address any one under the age of 13. We do not collect any personal information from children through our watch faces.
